This '''unnamed [[Human/Legends|Human]]''' was a member of the [[Korriban/Legends|Korriban]] spaceport's ground crew around [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. Along with the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Yas'tua]] and the [[Barabel/Legends|Barabel]] [[Rak'k]], he met [[Alema Rar]] when she landed at the spaceport in search of the [[One Sith|new Sith Order]]. When he refused to reveal their location, fearing for his life, Alema crushed his jaw using [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] and sent him stumbling into the port-master's office.

